data.description: Nestled in the peaceful Brandenburg neighborhood in St. Florian, this charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home offers charm and a cozy curated design. Every inch has been meticulously cared for and updated. This home offers an attached 2 car garage, a detached garage, and a workshop with a large acre lot which allows for endless storage or space for hobbies. Seize this rare opportunity and make this your home sweet home.
